
                          Java & REST

  What is it?
  -----------
  The project connects to the tweeter REST API, Application-only authentication,
  and download the last 50 tweets of a tweeter user.


  The Latest Version
  ------------------
  https://github.com/yes4me?tab=repositories
  Started on: Aug 16, 2015


  Documentation
  -------------
  Explication of the code is: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E8EYDH_KY6s

  Additional explication can be found at tweeter REST API:
  https://dev.twitter.com/oauth/application-only
  https://dev.twitter.com/rest/reference/get/statuses/user_timeline


  Installation
  ------------
  Install Java JDK
  Install Eclipse Java EE IDE for Web Developers
  Install Gradle plugin in Eclipse
  Run Twitter.java


